Class StanfordCoreNLPServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.StanfordCoreNLPServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class StanfordCoreNLPServer
extends Object
implements Runnable
    This class creates a server that runs a new Java annotator in each thread.
    Author:
    Gabor Angeli, Arun Chaganty
